  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc5\u0db9 \u0db1\u0d9c\u0dbb \u0dc3\u0db7\u0dcf \u2018\u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0da2\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u2019\u0da7 \u0d86\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0db7\u0ddd\u0d9c \u0dc0\u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0d87\u0dbb\u0db9\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Cultivation of food crops has started for Colombo Municipal Council's 'Community Kitchen'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The project to grow food crops on a part of the land where the Colombo Municipal Council building is located was carried out today (29) under the leadership of the Mayor Rosy Senanayake.",
        "Vegetable plants will be planted in a part of the municipal land, and this project will be implemented in collaboration with Cargill.",
        "Mayor Mrs. Rosy Senanayake said that the Colombo Municipal Council decided to start a plantation in the municipal area as a remedy for the economic crisis and food crisis in the country.",
        "She also said that she hopes to provide vegetables needed for the 'Community Kitchen' program, which has been started with the aim of providing meals to the poor people of Colombo city, from this plantation in the future."
      ],
